    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this absolutely pristine, mint-condition vehicle! It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot, with a flawless exterior and a spotless, like-new interior. This is a rare find for a buyer who demands the highest quality and a truly exceptional driving experience.",
